      "Native performance & smooth animations",
      "Implementation from provided UI designs",
      "App Store & Play Store deployment",
      "Post-launch maintenance & updates"
    ],
    badge: "MOST POPULAR",
    highlighted: true
  },
  {
    title: "Enterprise Mobile Apps",
    icon: "üè¢",
    desc: "Develop scalable enterprise-grade mobile applications with complex business logic, advanced features, and seamless user experiences.",
    features: [
      "Complex business logic implementation",
      "Third-party API integrations",
      "Real-time data synchronization",
      "Advanced security & authentication",
      "Performance optimization at scale"
    ],
    badge: "ENTERPRISE"
  },
  {
    title: "Web Development",
    icon: "üåê",
    desc: "Create modern, responsive web applications using cutting-edge frameworks. Perfect for landing pages, portfolios, and progressive web applications.",
    features: [
      "Responsive design for all devices",
      "SEO optimization & performance",
      "Modern framework implementation (Astro, React)",
      "Static site generation",
      "Analytics & tracking setup"
    ],
    badge: "NEW"
  },
  {
    title: "Code Optimization",
    icon: "‚ö°",
    desc: "Improve existing Flutter applications with performance optimization, code refactoring, and best practices implementation.",
    features: [
      "Performance analysis & optimization",
      "Code refactoring & clean architecture",
      "Memory leak detection & fixes",
      "UI/UX implementation improvements",
      "Testing & quality assurance"
    ]
  },
  {
    title: "Technical Consulting",
    icon: "üí°",
    desc: "Leverage my Flutter expertise to make informed decisions about your mobile app architecture, technology choices, and development roadmap.",
    features: [
      "Flutter architecture review",
      "Technology stack recommendations",
      "Code quality audits",
      "Performance optimization strategies",
      "Development best practices guidance"
    ]
  },
  {
    title: "Maintenance & Support",
    icon: "üõ†Ô∏è",
    desc: "Keep your Flutter applications running smoothly with ongoing maintenance, updates, and technical support when you need it most.",
    features: [
      "Bug fixes & issue resolution",
      "Flutter version upgrades",
